### High CPU Usage
1. Check PM2 processes: \`pm2 list\`
2. Check logs: \`~/view-logs.sh aplikasi1\`
3. Monitor in real-time: \`pm2 monit\`

### High Memory Usage
1. Restart application: \`pm2 restart aplikasi1\`
2. Check memory limit: \`pm2 describe aplikasi1\`
3. Check for memory leaks in app logs

